title: Police searching for armed robbery suspects
content: TAMPA -  Clearwater and Tampa police officers are on scene at Rocky Point off the Courtney Campbell Causeway searching for an armed robbery suspect.   Clearwater Police responded to a report of armed robbery at the AT&T store at 21561 US Highway 19N around 3:45pm this afternoon.    The suspects fled in a gray Nissan SUV.    A Clearwater Police officer spotted the suspect car eastbound on the Courtney Campbell Causeway a short time after the robbery. The officer monitored the car from a distance until additional law enforcement arrived on scene.    One suspect has been taken into custody but a second suspect is still at large.  Police helicopters are in the air searching for the suspect and police are searching cars before they leave the area.
